IN THE HIGH COURT OF PUNJAB AND HARYANA AT CHANDIGARH

HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE ASHUTOSH MOHUNTA.
PRESENT: MR. R.K. MALIK, ADVOCATE FOR THE PETITIONER.
MR. RAJEEV KWATRA, SR.DAG, HARYANA.
ASHUTOSH MOHUNTA, J. (ORAL)
Learned counsel for the petitioner states that this case has
already been decided by the Lok Adalat on 7.9.2001. A copy of the order of
the Lok Adalat has been placed on record.
As the matter has already been settled by the Lok Adalat,
therefore, no further orders are called for. The petition is accordingly
disposed of.
January 11, 2007
